residentes de la Iglesia: David O. McKay</a></cite>, 2003, pág. 15.</p></li><li data-marker=9. id=note9><p data-aid=141770117 id=note9_p1><a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.html?verse=19#p19" href="/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.19?lang=spa#p19">Mosíah 3:19</a>.</p></li><li data-marker=10. id=note10><p data-aid=141770121 id=note10_p1><a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/nt/rom/8.html?verse=5-6#p5" href="/scriptures/nt/rom/8.5-6?lang=spa#p5">Romanos 8:5–6</a>.</p></li><li data-marker=11. id=note11><p data-aid=141770127 id=note11_p1>Véase <a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/bofm/alma/34.html?verse=33#p33" href="/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.33?lang=spa#p33">Alma 34:33</a>.</p></li><li data-marker=12. id=note12><p data-aid=141770133 id=note12_p1>Russell M. Nelson, “<a class=cross-ref data-old-href="../../../general-conference/2019/04/36nelson.html?para=8#p8" href="/general-conference/2019/04/36nelson?lang=spa&para=8#p8">Podemos actuar mejor y ser mejores</a>”, <cite>Liahona,</cite> mayo de 2019, pág. 67.</p></li></ol></footer></div></article><div class=startHandle-2o_6p touch-action=none></div><div class=endHandle-wg4Dv touch-action=none></div></div></section></section><div class=mobileNav-1qobD><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobilePrev-1Jf8d" href="/study/liahona/2019/11/52boom?lang=spa"><button dir=ltr class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><span class=hiddenTitleText-2SahY></span><svg style=width:1.625rem;height:1.625rem viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-.003.751.751 0 0 1-.005 1.064L6.6 10.795h11.647c.403 0 .744.335.744.75 0 .417-.333.75-.744.75H6.565l5.74 5.739a.755.755 0 0 1 .004 1.065.751.751 0 0 1-1.065-.005l-6.71-6.709a.757.757 0 0 1-.127-.169.755.755 0 0 1-.416-.671c0-.31.184-.574.447-.689z"> </path></svg></button></a><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobileNext-1J33m